The paper deals with the task of extracting structured information from street view imagery using neural network models based on CNNs, RNNs, and attention mechanisms. This task falls under the domain of computer vision (cs.CV) and natural language processing (cs.CL). The use of neural networks and attention mechanisms also suggests that the paper may belong to the sub-categories of machine learning (cs.LG), information retrieval (cs.IR), and artificial intelligence (cs.AI).
